          "A FULL ITALIAN MEAL — the structure:",
          "",
          "   ANTIPASTO = starter",
          "      salumi, bruschette, olive",
          "   PRIMO = first course",
          "      pasta, risotto, soup",
          "   SECONDO = main course",
          "      meat or fish (no pasta!)",
          "   CONTORNO = side dish",
          "      vegetables, salad (separate!)",
          "   DOLCE = dessert",
          "      tiramisù, panna cotta, fruit",
          "   CAFFÈ = espresso to finish",
          "   DIGESTIVO = after-dinner liqueur",
          "",
          "You don't order all of these.",
          "Primo + secondo, or just a primo,",
          "is perfectly normal."
